Text:
Hi Stephen and Melissa,
The grill is scheduled to be delivered at the end of this month.
There are some special accessories that we ordered for you that will arrive earlier.
This is a combination housewarming gift and Christmas gift. Enjoy. Can't wait to see you at Christmas.
Love,
Mom and DaD
Thank you thank you thank you. House feels warmer with a grill. Christmas feels complete with a grill. Excited to slab some red meat on that thing when we get back from our trip:)
